text: The 3092 civil parishes (Portuguese: freguesias) of Portugal are listed In alphabetic groups (determined by a parish's first letter) in the template below. they are listed according to the following format: * Municipality ** Civil parish A complete and unbroken list of parishes all on one page is not available. A partial list is in :Category:Parishes of Portugal. Source: European Commission Portugal, Parishes Portugal 3 Parishes, Portugal Parishes *03
title: List of parishes of Portugal
